{"id":4222,"date":"2024-12-16T16:31:31","date_gmt":"2024-12-16T16:31:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=4222"},"modified":"2024-12-16T16:31:31","modified_gmt":"2024-12-16T16:31:31","slug":"macho-brace-upgrader","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/macho-brace-upgrader\/","title":{"rendered":"Macho Brace Upgrader (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Route 10<\/strong> &#8211; Standing next to a tree near the southern-most waterfall on Route 10, just south of the Cave of Being. Requires Surf<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Gives you a Macho Brace and upgrades it in exchange for Everstones<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>Everstones<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>Depends on the Macho Brace\u2019s level<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Fallshore City Pokemon Center and go west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-fallshore-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Fallshore City Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Fallshore City Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Approach the northwest exit of the city and continue following the linear path forward.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/02-pokemon-unbound-leaving-the-city-through-the-northwest-exit.jpg\" alt=\"Leaving the city through the northwest exit. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Leaving the city through the northwest exit.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually climb stairs to enter Route 10, indicating you\u2019re on the right path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/03-pokemon-unbound-climbing-the-stairs-to-route-10.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing the stairs to Route 10. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climbing the stairs to Route 10.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Start going south after crossing the first blue bridge on the route.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/04-pokemon-unbound-crossing-the-blue-bridge-and-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Crossing the blue bridge and going south. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Crossing the blue bridge and going south.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The path south will shortly run out. When it does, start surfing west on the water.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/05-pokemon-unbound-turning-west-when-the-path-south-ends.jpg\" alt=\"Turning west when the path south ends. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Turning west when the path south ends.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue on the path west and you\u2019ll see the Macho Brace Upgrade NPC standing next to a tree on a small patch of land. He\u2019s visible shortly after swimming past the top of a waterfall.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/06-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-macho-brace-upgrade-npc.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Macho Brace Upgrade NPC \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Macho Brace Upgrade NPC<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Purpose<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/07-pokemon-unbound-upgrading-the-macho-brace.jpg\" alt=\"Upgrading the Macho Brace. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Upgrading the Macho Brace.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Speaking with the Macho Brace Upgrade NPC for the first time rewards you with a free level 2 Macho Brace. After that, you can upgrade the Macho Brace by giving the NPC Everstones to increase the amount of Effort Values the Pokemon holding the brace gains.<\/p>\n<p>The table below details every Macho Brace upgrade, including the increase in EV gain and how many Everstones you need for each upgrade level.<\/p>\n<table class=\"table grey center zebra\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Macho Brace Level<\/th>\n<th>Everstone Cost<\/th>\n<th>EV Gain<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>3<\/td>\n<td>3 Everstones<\/td>\n<td>3x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4<\/td>\n<td>4 Everstones<\/td>\n<td>4x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5<\/td>\n<td>5 Everstones<\/td>\n<td>5x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6<\/td>\n<td>6 Everstones<\/td>\n<td>6x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7<\/td>\n<td>7 Everstones<\/td>\n<td>7x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8<\/td>\n<td>8 Everstones<\/td>\n<td>8x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9<\/td>\n<td>9 Everstones<\/td>\n<td>9x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<td>10 Everstones<\/td>\n<td>10x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Useful NPCs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":4223,"parent":2143,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[],"class_list":["post-4222","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/4222","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/2143"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4223"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4222"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4222"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}